   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> La Pittura </s>
            </p>
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata - N. 1043 </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>La Pittura</head>
               <figDesc> Due bambini rovesciano dell' inchiostro su di un cane
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Modena lì 8/6 - 917</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Sempre gli sguardi ed i pensieri <lb/>            rivolti là, verso la rosea nube degli<lb/>            ideali, in un cielo azzurro cristal - <lb/>            lino che non paventa la bufera,<lb/>            in una esaltazione di purezza<lb/>            in una tranquillità di moti. <lb/>            Un delizioso bacio e fine <gap reason="illegible"/>epibile<lb/>            mistero che unisce i nostri cuori. </p>
                  <p type="fronte">
                     <lb/>            Finisce la serie poco seria delle arti belle.<lb/>            Saluti alla mamma e a tutti. </p>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>
                  <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="address-destination">
               <p>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>
                        <lb/>            Gent Sig.na<lb/>            Oliva Turtura <lb/>            Via Girolamo Rosfi 58 <lb/>            Ravenna</addrLine>
                  </address>
               </p>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 97 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
